Welcome to ViewDiz - An advanced description viewer and manipulator.
Copyright ©1997-1998 by Mikael Lund

@{b}@{u}Please chose an issue:@{ub}@{uu}

@{"    Introduction   " link "Intro"}  What is it ?
@{" File descriptions " link "Descriptions"}  Story about descriptions.

